item.title: [HIVE-20508] Hive does not support user names of type "user@realm"
item.description: Hive does not support user names of type "user@realm". This causes authorization problems with Ranger for user names containing realms in Kerberos environment.
item.summary: Hive does not support user names of type "user@realm"
